    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ちょっ！　何を言っているんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! What are you saying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8703179996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "わわ、私は緊張なんてする訳にゃいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm not nervous at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6703180234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.0036513329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "にゃい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0036513329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.3703169823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うるさいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're annoying!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3703169823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "緊張するのは悪いことではないのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being nervous isn't a bad thing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1369836728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.636983649
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そうだね。緊張してるのはみんな同じ、だよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ that's right. We're all nervous‚ aren't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.636983649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3703169823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それより、{user}さんとさとみさんを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More importantly‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3703169823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "置いてけぼりにしていますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you're leaving {user}-san and Satomi-san behind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9369836728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.0036503156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わわっ、ほんとだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wow‚ you're right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0036503156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、琴乃ちゃん、どうぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ Kotono-chan‚ go ahead!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1036503394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9036477725
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ちょ、渚！　急に振らないでよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait‚ Nagisa! Don't just suddenly pass it over to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9036477725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3666672706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ごほん。改めて、ご覧いただきありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahem. Once again‚ thank you for watching",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1666672706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.2675938447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "今回私達はデビュー曲である『月下儚美』を選びました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ we chose our debut song‚ \"Night-blooming Beauty\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2675938447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.456323719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "パフォーマンスで感謝を伝える……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Expressing gratitude through performance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.456323719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "凄く難しいねってみんなで話し合ったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We discussed it with everyone‚ and it seemed very difficult",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.089658602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7896570523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかんだいって意見は一致しましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But in the end‚ we all agreed‚ didn't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7896570523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.0229903857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最初のライブからの成長を見せることが一番の感謝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Showing growth from the first live is the greatest gratitude",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0229903857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "だよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7229919354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1229883511
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あー！　私が言おうと思いましたのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh! I was going to say that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1229883511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁでも、そういうことですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ that's how it is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.689658602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.4563216845
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "嬉しい時は{user}さんやさとみさん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we're happy‚ {user}-san‚ and Satomi-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4563216845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで喜びを分かち合って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We share the joy together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8666672706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.1896550178
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "つ、辛い時にはいつもそばにいてくれたことには",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-And when it's tough‚ I'm grateful for",
